    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此 RIFTSTORM 试玩版精选自完整体验。玩家将立即投入战斗，使用 4 名满级 Weavers 并搭配简化版制作系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了突出重点，任务池已限制为四个精心挑选的行动，展示了地下城探索、生存撤离和首领突袭的混合玩法——让您初尝即将到来的挑战与混乱。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About RIFTSTORM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >风暴来了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个充斥着神话、传说和无尽恐怖的宇宙中，地球不过是一个渺小微不足道的球体，正面临着来自那些超越人类理解之物的持续不断威胁。来自其他世界和维度的Rifts威胁要吞噬我们。来自内部和外部的怪物超越了人类的理解。尽管人类的力量相形见绌，但掌握rift原始能量的人将获得无法衡量的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 RIFTSTORM 中，您将扮演精英特工 Weaver，其任务是关闭 Rifts 并遏制 mythic 威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻求这个世界的黑暗与未知真相者，必须遵守Mythic Protocol的规则。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到 Protocol</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/a1728c703a93d82274c05815850fd32a.poster.avif?t=1749878297\" width=568 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/a1728c703a93d82274c05815850fd32a.webm?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/a1728c703a93d82274c05815850fd32a.mp4?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强大的秘密结社都服从于Mythic Protocol，这是一个搜寻、收容并整理海量mythic未知事物的组织。你将在其荫蔽下执行任务，保护世界免受极少数人知晓、更少人理解的威胁。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>出击，搜刮，重复</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/3987947a1e07baf52494f8906035714b.poster.avif?t=1749878297\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/3987947a1e07baf52494f8906035714b.webm?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/3987947a1e07baf52494f8906035714b.mp4?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集蕴含神秘组织超自然科技的武器库。为你的Weavers找到或打造完美武器，并调整其玩法，以应对你在战场上可能遇到的任何mythic挑战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遵循 Protocols，遏制威胁</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/fdd013f54d7d3b4e1433bb13d05cc14b.poster.avif?t=1749878297\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/fdd013f54d7d3b4e1433bb13d05cc14b.webm?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/fdd013f54d7d3b4e1433bb13d05cc14b.mp4?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mythics 潜伏在我们世界的黑暗角落，形态万千。每个物种都带来独特的挑战和危险，要想对抗它们，就必须了解保卫我们世界的 Protocols。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>编织强大能力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/7984dc209ec14a353f7b9b89520f2339.poster.avif?t=1749878297\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/7984dc209ec14a353f7b9b89520f2339.webm?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/7984dc209ec14a353f7b9b89520f2339.mp4?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从不断壮大的Weavers（拥有关闭Rifts力量的精英特工）队伍中进行选择。每位Weaver都来自Mythic Protocol组织的各个部门，拥有独特的技能和玩法风格，体现了该组织内每个单位的特点。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>适应并进化您的 Weavers</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/45b413d1712fd3e64b5ed11235c99ef7.poster.avif?t=1749878297\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/45b413d1712fd3e64b5ed11235c99ef7.webm?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/45b413d1712fd3e64b5ed11235c99ef7.mp4?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过我们独特的Periapts，你可以打造属于你自己的Weaver，并重塑精调他们的Weavers’技能和能力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>任务各不相同</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/6eb0bb3475a5fc7e1249fc88c951f916.poster.avif?t=1749878297\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/6eb0bb3475a5fc7e1249fc88c951f916.webm?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/6eb0bb3475a5fc7e1249fc88c951f916.mp4?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组合超过 100 种不同的 lythogram 强化，每次任务都会发现不同的组合。Lythograms 会给你的 Weavers 提供广泛的增益和修正，确保拥有多样化的游玩风格和协同作用。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与朋友畅玩全球</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/85b0666e79c3b5b7e9b749ef42484a18.poster.avif?t=1749878297\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/85b0666e79c3b5b7e9b749ef42484a18.webm?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212570/extras/85b0666e79c3b5b7e9b749ef42484a18.mp4?t=1749878297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅仅是一支被动的应变部队，你可以独自或与最多两名好友一同部署，追逐Rifts和Mythics，揭示未知谜团。每个任务目标都对世界以及你身处其中的位置有着更大的影响。</p>",
